Clara Beyers https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clara_Beyers 0 Clara Beyers (c.1880 - c.1950?) was an American silent film stock actress She was signed in 1913 and starred in 32 films before her retirement from film in 1922. She starred with William Garwood in films such as His Picture.
